{"tid":2287591,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"周梓樂死因研訊今展開 預計需時5周將傳逾60證人","createTime":"2020-11-16T01:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T01:27:56.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"41f908cf5253c3f254edd1d4d810a3616d5b2afe","tid":2287591,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T01:08:58.000Z","msg":"科大生周梓樂去年11月，在將軍澳尚德停車場墮樓，留院5天後不治，終年22歲。周梓樂墮樓及受傷的原因一直成謎，引起外界揣測，死因庭今就事件展開研訊，預計需時5星期，將傳召60多名證人，包括現場市民、警員、消防員、法醫、負責診治的醫生，以及骨科和鑑證專家。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/684f7ca29bc1d254a9bcbe4ebfa8a8e6/stheadline/inewsmedia/20201116/_2020111608540250197.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F684f7ca29bc1d254a9bcbe4ebfa8a8e6%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20201116%2F_2020111608540250197.jpg&h=4efe83ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline. com/news/realtime/hk/1924708</code></pre>"},{"pid":"d29f2cfaa7085bbf1091a19dba99650fb7789144","tid":2287591,"uid":255976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T01:12:36.000Z","msg":"導演是低智森嗎?"},{"pid":"53e5b858b81719f8a789c6b36361913aaea452bf","tid":2287591,"uid":272565,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T01:19:04.000Z","msg":"最後可能只係「不合法被殺」就close file。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea3cdd3c0317847166dc8c085edfbff96a84186","tid":2287591,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"53e5b858b81719f8a789c6b36361913aaea452bf","tid":2287591,"uid":272565,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T01:19:04.000Z","msg":"最後可能只係「不合法被殺」就close file。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T01:21:01.000Z","msg":"係, 所以哂心機捱眼瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ae1088cb4188432baf50a4d7c7f4ef9ed9f79